And this here and here.
还有这里跟这里

48:29.320 --> 48:30.830
- Okay.  - And the windows.
-可以  -还有窗

48:33.360 --> 48:37.950
-Get me a phone with a scrambler.   -A scrambler.
-还有一支有防窃听的电话  -防窃听器

48:38.040 --> 48:40.500
And a radio with scanners
还有无线电扫描仪

48:40.640 --> 48:42.590
to pick up flying saucers, stuff like that.
好扫描飞碟出没，像这样的东西

48:42.680 --> 48:44.310
Don't forget the fog lights.
别忘了雾灯

48:44.480 --> 48:48.350
Oh. In case I get caught in a swamp. That's a good idea.
以防我被困在沼泽里，好主意

48:51.480 --> 48:54.470
Get out of the way, lady! I'm trying to drive here!
让路，女士！我在开车！

48:55.840 --> 48:58.220
I thought you were taking me to Frank.
我以为你要载我去找法兰克

49:03.840 --> 49:06.350
We got an hour. You hungry?
还有一个小时，你饿吗？

49:08.080 --> 49:09.870
No, but I'm bored.
不饿，但是很无聊

49:10.920 --> 49:12.510
Well, that figures.
我就知道

49:14.720 --> 49:18.030
Check it out, Manny, okay? And pay the guy.
你来搞定，曼尼？付他钱

49:18.320 --> 49:21.550
And you take a taxi. Meet me at the track, okay?
你自己搭出租车，和我在跑马场碰头，可以吗？

49:21.720 --> 49:23.350
-Good doing business with you.   -Mr. Montana.
-很高兴和你做生意  -蒙大拿先生

49:24.800 --> 49:26.230
Oh, God, man!
噢，老天！

49:28.840 --> 49:31.190
I wouldn't buy the car if you didn't like it.
如果你不喜欢这辆车，我就不会买

49:31.360 --> 49:34.070
Planning on driving the girls crazy, aren't you, Tony?
想让女孩为你晕头转向，对吧，东尼？

49:34.240 --> 49:36.430
Oh, yeah. You know who?
你知道是谁吗？

49:38.560 --> 49:40.350
What would Frank say?
法兰克会怎么说？

49:42.720 --> 49:44.390
I like Frank, you know?
我喜欢法兰克，你呢？

49:44.960 --> 49:46.750
Only I like you better.
只是我更喜欢你

49:54.600 --> 49:56.950
-You got some for me?   -Sure.
-分我一点？ -好啊

50:04.640 --> 50:05.750
Okay.
好

50:12.240 --> 50:13.430
Okay.
好

50:15.280 --> 50:20.030
Don't get confused, Tony. I don't fuck around with the help.
别搞错，东尼，我不和下人乱搞

50:27.600 --> 50:31.430
You wanna play that way with me, I play with you.
你想和我玩游戏，我就和你玩

50:31.560 --> 50:32.750
Shit.
狗屎

50:33.400 --> 50:35.110
Would you kiss me if I wear the hat?
如果我带帽子，你会亲我吗？

50:35.240 --> 50:36.270
No!
不会！

50:38.560 --> 50:40.790
Playtime is over, okay?
游戏时间结束了，懂吗？

50:43.440 --> 50:44.630
Okay.
好

51:38.000 --> 51:39.310
Mama?
妈妈？

51:41.000 --> 51:42.310
Antonio.
安东尼奥

51:42.640 --> 51:43.860
Long time.
好久不见

51:46.680 --> 51:48.470
No postcards from jail, huh?
在牢里都不写信回来？

51:59.320 --> 52:00.460
Gina.
吉娜

52:02.200 --> 52:05.070
-Tony?   -Look at you.
-东尼？ -看看你

52:07.000 --> 52:08.550
You're beautiful.
你真美

52:09.200 --> 52:11.990
-I didn't...   -Mama, look at those eyes, huh.
-我没…  -妈妈，看她那双眼睛

52:12.200 --> 52:14.430
Look at that. She looks like me.
你看，她跟我好像

52:15.200 --> 52:18.030
You know the last time I saw you, you was like that.
上次我见到你的时候，你才这么大

52:18.160 --> 52:21.670
You looked like a little boy. Now look at you.
像个小男生，现在你看看

52:26.040 --> 52:27.870
I got something for you.
我有东西给你

52:33.080 --> 52:34.910
It's no big deal.
只是个小东西

52:36.920 --> 52:37.900
Oh, Tony!
东尼！

52:49.560 --> 52:51.790
I never thought I'd see you again, you know?
我以为再也见不到你了，你知道吗？

52:51.920 --> 52:53.990
You think they'd keep a guy like me down?
你以为他们能关得住我吗？

52:54.080 --> 52:55.630
Well, no.
才不

52:59.920 --> 53:04.860
-You look so good.   -Look, open that up. Open it.
-你看来很好  -打开来看，打开

53:05.560 --> 53:07.790
-For me?   -I think so.
-给我的？ -应该是

53:09.080 --> 53:12.430
It's nothing much, you know, nothing.
只是个小东西，你知道，不算什么

53:17.400 --> 53:18.910
See what's written on the back?
看看后面写了什么？

53:19.000 --> 53:20.310
On the back? Aw.
后面？

53:20.440 --> 53:22.110
东尼送给吉娜，直到永远

53:22.240 --> 53:26.110
-Always.   -"Always." It's beautiful, Tony!
-直到永远  -“直到永远”，真美，东尼！

53:27.760 --> 53:29.830
Mama is still working in the factory,
妈妈还在工厂工作

53:29.960 --> 53:32.030
and I work part-time in a beauty parlor.
我在美容院打工

53:32.120 --> 53:35.230
I'm doing hair, Tony. Do you remember Hiram Gonzalez?
我是美发师，东尼，你还记得海瑞工萨尔吗？

53:35.480 --> 53:38.190
His father owned that barbershop. It's his place.
那间理发院是他爸爸开的，是他的地方

53:38.280 --> 53:40.950
Plus I go to junior college. Miami Dade.
而且我在读短期大学，在迈阿密戴德

53:41.120 --> 53:44.110
In two more years, I get my cosmetology license.
再两年，我就可以拿到美容师牌照

53:44.280 --> 53:47.510
-Then I'll be making enough money...   -Surprise!
-然后我就会赚够钱…  -惊喜一下！

53:48.160 --> 53:50.830
All that's over, starting today.
全都结束了，从今天开始

53:51.320 --> 53:52.300
Why?
为什么？

53:52.440 --> 53:57.110
My kid sister don't have to work in no beauty parlor, and Mama,
我的小妹妹不需要在美容院做事，我妈也是

53:57.680 --> 54:00.140
she don't have to sew in no factory.
她不需要在工厂做衣服了

54:00.440 --> 54:02.510
Your son made it, Mama.
你儿子办到了，妈

54:04.000 --> 54:05.310
He's a success.
他成功了

54:06.480 --> 54:08.860
That's why I didn't come around before.
这就是为什么我前一阵子都没来

54:09.840 --> 54:13.710
I want you to see what a good boy I've been.
我要你看看我现在有多吃得开

54:16.160 --> 54:17.630
Here's $1,000.
这里是一千块

54:18.400 --> 54:19.830
For you, Mama.
给你的，妈妈

54:27.680 --> 54:30.350
-Who did you kill for this, Antonio?   -Mama.
-这是杀了什么人赚到的，东尼？  -妈

54:30.720 --> 54:32.670
I didn't kill nobody, Mama.
我没杀人，妈

54:33.640 --> 54:34.700
- No?   - No.
-没有？  -没有

54:35.720 --> 54:37.670
What are you doing now?
你现在在做什么？

54:38.320 --> 54:41.350
Banks, or is it still bodegas, you and the others?
你和其它人现在是抢银行，还是小杂货店？

54:41.480 --> 54:43.670
No! Things are different now.
不是！现在不一样了

54:43.840 --> 54:46.630
I'm working with an anti-Castro group.
我和反卡斯特罗集团合作

54:47.040 --> 54:48.590
I'm an organizer now.
我现在负责组织筹划

54:48.720 --> 54:51.020
I get a lot of political contributions.
我做了很多政治贡献

54:52.040 --> 54:53.550
Sure you do.
说得好听

54:58.000 --> 55:01.030
A gun sticking in somebody's face is how.
靠把枪指在别人头上赚钱

55:02.720 --> 55:05.710
You know, all we hear about in the papers
我们在报纸上看得多了

55:07.560 --> 55:10.510
is animals like you and the killings.
都是像你这样的禽兽跟杀人案

55:11.240 --> 55:14.470
It's Cubans like you who are giving a bad name to our people,
就是像你这样的古巴人，把我们人民的名声搞臭了

55:14.560 --> 55:17.870
people who come here, work hard and make a good name for themselves.
那些来这里勤奋工作，为自己建立了好名声的人

55:18.040 --> 55:19.990
People who send their children to school.
那些送孩子们去上学的人

55:20.080 --> 55:21.710
What are you saying? That's your son...
你在说什么？那是你儿子…

55:21.880 --> 55:24.910
Son? I wish I had one.
儿子？我有儿子吗？

55:25.720 --> 55:26.750
-He's a bum.   -No.
-他是痞子  -不

55:26.920 --> 55:29.750
He was a bum then and he's a bum now.
他以前是个痞子，现在也是个痞子

55:31.760 --> 55:33.510
Who do you think you are?
你以为你是谁？

55:36.080 --> 55:39.030
We haven't heard a word from you in five years.
五年来，只字片语都没有

55:42.080 --> 55:44.830
You suddenly show up here, throw some money around
现在突然出现，拿钱砸人

55:44.920 --> 55:47.380
and think you can get my respect.
以为这样我就会看得起你

55:47.920 --> 55:50.670
You think you can buy me with jewelry?
你以为可以用珠宝买通我？

55:50.760 --> 55:54.350
You think you can come into my house with your hotshot clothes
你以为你可以穿名牌衣服到我家

55:54.440 --> 55:56.900
and your jail manners and make fun of us?
用你在牢里学的态度来嘲笑我们？

55:57.080 --> 56:01.190
-You don't know what you're saying.   -That's not the way I am, Antonio!
-你不知道自己在说什么  -我不是哪种人，安东尼奥！

56:01.400 --> 56:03.910
That is not the way I raised Gina to be!
那也不是我教养吉娜的方式！

56:06.040 --> 56:08.420
You are not going to destroy her.
你不准毁了她

56:10.120 --> 56:11.910
I don't need your money.
我不需要你的钱

56:13.960 --> 56:15.790
I work for my living.
我自己会赚钱

56:16.360 --> 56:18.950
I don't want you in this house anymore!
我不要你再出现在我家！

56:19.400 --> 56:21.350
I don't want you around Gina.
我不要你接近吉娜

56:22.280 --> 56:24.950
So come on. Get out!
所以，滚出去！

56:31.120 --> 56:32.100
Okay.
好

56:35.640 --> 56:36.750
Mama...
妈妈…

56:36.840 --> 56:40.830
And take this lousy money with you. It stinks.
把你的脏钱拿走，臭死了

56:41.160 --> 56:42.270
Tony.
东尼

56:43.560 --> 56:46.430
Why do you have to spoil it for everybody, huh?
你为什么非让大家都难过不可？

56:49.080 --> 56:50.750
I'm sorry, Tony.
对不起，东尼

56:52.480 --> 56:53.830
Okay, Mama.
好吧，妈妈

56:58.160 --> 56:59.670
No. Tony, wait a minute!
东尼，等等！

56:59.760 --> 57:01.910
-Don't go, please!   -Gina, stay here!
-别走，拜托！ -吉娜，站住！

57:02.160 --> 57:04.270
-No, Mama.   -He's no good. Gina!
-别这样，妈妈  -他没救了，吉娜！

57:05.600 --> 57:07.430
Tony, wait, please!
东尼，等等，拜托！

57:08.000 --> 57:12.510
I'm sorry. I don't know. Mama, ever since Papa left, she's...
对不起，我不知道自从爸爸走了之后，妈妈她…

57:12.600 --> 57:14.750
Forget Papa. We never had one.
忘了爸爸吧，我们没有爸爸

57:14.960 --> 57:17.520
I know you did some bad things back then.
我知道你在那边做过不好的事

57:17.760 --> 57:20.430
In the Army, I know you got into some trouble.
在军队里，我知道你遇到麻烦

57:20.520 --> 57:22.270
The Communists,
共产党

57:22.360 --> 57:24.430
they're always trying to tell you what to do.
他们总是试图告诉你该怎么做

57:24.520 --> 57:27.350
-Mama doesn't understand that.  -I know.
-妈妈并不了解这些  -我知道

57:29.040 --> 57:31.600
I just... I don't know.
我只是…我也不知道

57:31.680 --> 57:34.270
I just want you to know that I don't care.
我只是想让你知道，我不在乎那些

57:34.520 --> 57:38.430
It doesn't matter to me how long you've been away, five or ten years.
不论你离开多久，五年也好，十年也好，我都不在乎

57:40.560 --> 57:43.710
You're my blood, always.
你是我的至亲，永远都是

57:44.920 --> 57:47.510
I know.
我知道

57:56.560 --> 57:59.750
-Come on. I want you to take this.   -I gotta go back in.
-来吧，我要你拿去  -我必须回去了

57:59.880 --> 58:02.550
-No, Tony. Please.  -You need this.
-别这样，东尼，拜托  -你需要这个

58:02.680 --> 58:03.990
What will I tell her?
我要怎么跟她说？

58:04.080 --> 58:05.790
Take that. You don't tell her anything.
拿去，什么都别跟她说

58:05.880 --> 58:09.420
Don't tell her I gave it to you, but give her some from time to time.
别说是我给你的，但是隔一段时间就拿一些给她

58:09.560 --> 58:12.150
And listen, you go out yourself.
听好，你自己要出去玩

58:12.240 --> 58:15.710
Go ahead. Go out, do some things. Have some fun.
出去找点事做，玩得开心一点

58:15.880 --> 58:17.990
You gotta get some fun out of life.
你一定要享受人生的乐趣

58:18.080 --> 58:20.910
You gonna beat yourself to death at 19?
你不想19岁就过劳死吧？

58:21.040 --> 58:23.550
A pussycat like you? Come here.
像你这么漂亮的女生？过来

58:27.920 --> 58:29.790
-I'll talk to you again.   -Okay.
-我们以后再聊  -好

58:29.920 --> 58:31.990
Put that money away. Don't let her see it.
把钱收好，别被她看到了

58:32.080 --> 58:33.590
I'll talk to her.
我会和她谈谈

58:35.560 --> 58:36.910
-I'll talk to you.  -Okay.
-我们以后再聊  -好

58:39.080 --> 58:40.140
Let's go.
走吧

58:42.160 --> 58:44.750
-She's beautiful. How come you...   -Hey!
-她真漂亮，你怎么… -嘿！

58:47.280 --> 58:51.270
Stay away from her. You hear?
离她远点，听到没？

58:52.120 --> 58:54.790
-She's not for you.   -Okay.
-别打她主意  -知道了

59:02.640 --> 59:08.110
COCHABAMBA, BOLIVIA
玻利维亚 科恰班巴

59:20.240 --> 59:23.310
So, this and my other factory, I can guarantee production
这间工厂加上我的工厂，我可以保证

59:23.400 --> 59:27.470
of 200 kilos refined every month of the year.
每个月生产两百公斤纯古柯碱

59:27.920 --> 59:30.190
The problem is, I have no steady market.
问题是我没有稳定的市场

59:30.280 --> 59:33.670
Basically, what I'm looking for is somebody in the States
基本上我需要的是一个在美国

59:33.760 --> 59:37.150
who can share the risk with me, somebody who can guarantee
可以和我分担风险的人，一个可以保证

59:37.240 --> 59:41.430
to buy from me, say, 150 kilos a month.
每个月跟我买一百五十公斤货的人

59:42.920 --> 59:46.150
Oh, that's a big commitment, Mr. Sosa. Something like that...
这是个很大的承诺，索沙先生，像这样的…

59:47.240 --> 59:49.590
Too bad Frank's not here. You should talk to him.
法兰克不在真是太糟了，你应该和他谈谈

59:49.680 --> 59:52.750
-It would've been nice if he'd come.   -He would like to come,
-如果他能来就好了 -他很想来

59:52.840 --> 59:57.430
but with his trial coming up, it's hard to leave the country.
但是他的案子就快开庭了，不方便出国

59:57.520 --> 01:00:00.910
-So he sent you instead?   -Something like that.
-所以他派你来？ -差不多

01:00:01.000 --> 01:00:03.270
We'll talk at my house, shall we?
我们到我家谈，好吗？

01:00:03.880 --> 01:00:07.310
You got good stuff here. Class-A shit.
你的东西不错，上等货色

01:00:29.160 --> 01:00:32.910
This Lopez guarantees to buy 150 kilos from me
罗培兹保证每个月跟我买

01:00:33.000 --> 01:00:34.270
every month of the year.
一百五十公斤的货

01:00:34.400 --> 01:00:35.590
He picks it up here.
接下来就由他搞定

01:00:35.680 --> 01:00:37.910
I can sell it to him for as little as
我最便宜可以卖他

01:00:39.840 --> 01:00:43.310
7,000 a key. You can't do better than that.
一公斤七千元，不可能再更便宜了

01:00:44.160 --> 01:00:46.950
But then we got to take the risk of moving it.
但是我们要承担运送的风险

01:00:47.200 --> 01:00:50.150
We'll be cutting out the Colombians. Know what that means?
我们也会踢走哥伦比亚人，你知道这代表什么吗？

01:00:50.240 --> 01:00:52.150
That means we have to go to war with them.
这代表我们和他们开战

01:00:52.240 --> 01:00:55.780
We cut out the Colombians, we take risks on both sides.
我们踢走哥伦比亚人，我们承担双重风险

01:00:55.920 --> 01:00:57.750
Why don't we split the risk?
我们何不平分风险？

01:00:59.440 --> 01:01:02.980
You guarantee your delivery, say, as far as Panama,
你保证货会运到巴拿马

01:01:03.840 --> 01:01:05.550
we take it from there.
我们从那里接手

01:01:07.920 --> 01:01:11.310
Panama is risky. It costs me more.
巴拿马风险太高了，会增加我的成本

01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:17.230
Panama I can sell for 13.5 a key.
巴拿马的话，一公斤我要卖一万三千五百元

01:01:18.520 --> 01:01:21.030
13.5? What, are you nuts?
一万三千五百元？你疯了吗？

01:01:22.640 --> 01:01:26.260
13.5? We still got to take that shit to Florida.
一万三千五百元？我们还得把东西运到佛罗里达

01:01:26.360 --> 01:01:28.470
Do you know what that's like these days?
你知道最近是什么状况吗？

01:01:28.560 --> 01:01:30.630
You got the Navy everywhere.
到处都是海军

01:01:30.800 --> 01:01:35.150
You got frogmen. You got EC2s with the satellite-tracking shit.
有蛙人，还有装了雷达追踪器的军舰

01:01:35.760 --> 01:01:39.030
You got the fucking Bell 209 assault choppers up the ass.
还有他妈的攻击直升机在上方飞

01:01:39.520 --> 01:01:42.030
We're losing one out of every nine loads.
九批货就有一批被抄到

01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:45.910
That's no duckwalk anymore, let me tell you.
事情没那么容易了，我告诉你

01:01:46.120 --> 01:01:47.550
Forget about 13.5.
一万三千五百是不可能的

01:01:51.120 --> 01:01:53.870
What do you suggest that is reasonable?
那你说多少才合理？

01:01:59.480 --> 01:02:01.510
Excuse me. One moment.
抱歉，稍等一下

01:02:05.960 --> 01:02:08.310
What the fuck's the matter with you?
你在搞什么鬼？

01:02:08.400 --> 01:02:10.030
Are you negotiating for Frank Lopez?
你是在帮法兰克罗培兹谈判吗？

01:02:10.160 --> 01:02:12.390
Don't worry about it. Take it easy.
别担心，放轻松

01:02:12.480 --> 01:02:15.510
I'm not worried about it. You should worry about it.
我没担心，你才应该担心

01:02:16.120 --> 01:02:18.950
If he wants to make a deal, it's up to him, not you.
如果他想谈成生意，他说了算，不是你

01:02:19.040 --> 01:02:20.590
We're doing this one deal. That's it.
我们只做这一笔，就一次

