-他知道怎么对待女人？  -对

01:28:45.920 --> 01:28:47.990
By taking her to the toilet to make out?
把人家带到厕所去胡搞？

01:28:48.080 --> 01:28:52.110
You've been a great audience. I got a special treat for you.
你是个很好的听众，我有个特别的奖励给你

01:28:52.240 --> 01:28:53.790
Here's a guy I found in the jungle
他是我在委内瑞拉的加拉加斯

01:28:53.920 --> 01:28:56.750
from Caracas, Venezuela. He's unlike anything you've seen.
丛林里找到的，和你们以前见过的完全不同

01:28:56.840 --> 01:29:00.460
Give a warm Babylon welcome to the one and only Octavio!
让我们用热烈欢迎绝无仅有的奥克特维奥！

01:29:26.160 --> 01:29:29.350
Look around. Go out with someone who has something on the ball,
四周围看看，和一些成功的人出去玩

01:29:29.440 --> 01:29:32.110
-who's going somewhere in life.   -Like who?
-有正常生活的人 -像是谁？

01:29:32.840 --> 01:29:36.190
For instance, someone who's got a real job, like a banker.
像是一个有正常工作的人，像是银行员

01:29:36.280 --> 01:29:39.150
-Or... Or a doctor, a lawyer...   -What about you?
-或是…或是医生、律师…  -那你呢？

01:29:41.640 --> 01:29:44.750
-What are you talking about?    -Why don't you take me out?
-你在说什么？  -你为什么不约我出去？

01:29:44.840 --> 01:29:46.750
Are you crazy?
你疯了吗？

01:29:46.840 --> 01:29:48.830
I see the way you look at me, Manolo.
我看过你看我的眼神，马诺洛

01:29:49.120 --> 01:29:51.950
-Do you think I'm blind? I see.   -Come on.
-你以为我是瞎子吗？我看得见  -拜托

01:29:52.480 --> 01:29:54.390
-What?    -Look, Gina,
-怎样？  -看，吉娜

01:29:55.880 --> 01:29:58.510
Tony and I are like brothers, all right?
东尼和我就像兄弟一样，知道吗？

01:29:58.880 --> 01:30:00.510
You're his kid sister.
你是他妹妹

01:30:00.640 --> 01:30:02.310
-So what?    -That's where it ends.
-那又怎样？  -就这样而已

01:30:03.080 --> 01:30:06.190
-That's where it stays.   -Are you afraid of Tony, huh?
-就只能是这样   -你怕东尼吗？

01:30:07.160 --> 01:30:10.630
-You afraid of Tony's kid sister?   -I'm not afraid of anybody!
-你怕东尼的妹妹吗？  -我谁也不怕！

01:30:11.000 --> 01:30:12.870
That's not the point here!
这不是重点！

01:32:28.720 --> 01:32:29.700
Oh, fuck.
妈的

01:32:31.520 --> 01:32:33.470
It's not for me. Don't look at me.
不是找我的，别看我

01:32:33.560 --> 01:32:36.630
-How do you know?   -'Cause I'm not here.
-你怎么知道？  -因为我不在这里

01:32:36.720 --> 01:32:38.630
Oh, really? Then where are you?
真的？那你在哪里？

01:32:41.640 --> 01:32:43.150
Shit, you're weird.
你这个怪人

01:32:43.240 --> 01:32:45.540
-I'm weird?   -Hello?
-我怪吗？  -喂？

01:32:45.640 --> 01:32:48.070
-Hello, Miriam?   -Tony!
-蜜莉安？ -东尼！

01:32:48.160 --> 01:32:51.390
-Put Manny on, okay?   -Okay. Just a second.
-叫曼尼听电话，好吗？  -等一下

01:32:51.720 --> 01:32:53.030
It's Tony.
是东尼

01:32:56.040 --> 01:32:58.270
What are you doing, checking up on me?
你在干嘛？在查我吗？

01:32:58.360 --> 01:33:00.190
Get your clothes on and meet me
穿好衣服，45分钟之后

01:33:00.320 --> 01:33:02.190
in front of Lopez Motors in 45 minutes.
到罗培兹汽车经销店外跟我碰头

01:33:03.000 --> 01:33:06.190
-What? What happened?   -Nothing we can't fix.
-什么？怎么了？ -没有我们处理不了的事

01:33:06.840 --> 01:33:09.190
All right. I'll be there.
好，我立刻到

01:33:09.320 --> 01:33:11.910
You're still on the phone. Let's go.
你还在电话上，动作快

01:33:12.000 --> 01:33:13.110
Take it easy, okay?
别紧张，好吗？

01:33:13.200 --> 01:33:16.070
I'm leaving now. Fuck.
我现在就走，妈的

01:33:16.680 --> 01:33:18.310
-Nick?    -Yeah, Tony.
-尼克？  -是，东尼

01:33:18.400 --> 01:33:20.700
This is what I want you to do for me,
我要你帮我做件事

01:33:22.160 --> 01:33:23.910
you call Lopez.
打给罗培兹

01:33:24.440 --> 01:33:28.140
Call him at his office at 3:00 sharp.
三点整打到他的办公室给他

01:33:29.040 --> 01:33:31.910
And you tell him,
你跟他说

01:33:33.080 --> 01:33:35.230
"We fucked up, he got away."
“我们搞砸了，他逃走了”

01:33:35.920 --> 01:33:38.430
-Okay. Yeah.   -Got it? What are you going to say?
-好  -懂了吗？你该说什么？

01:33:38.520 --> 01:33:40.430
"We fucked up. He got away."
“我们搞砸了，他逃走了”

01:33:42.280 --> 01:33:43.950
-What time?    -3:00 sharp.
-几点？  -三点整

01:33:46.160 --> 01:33:48.870
So when are we gonna make some money on this thing?
这件事我们什么时候可以开始赚到钱？

01:33:49.000 --> 01:33:51.950
Six months to start don't mean shit, Larry.
说就说六个月

01:33:52.560 --> 01:33:55.830
I'm not a Rockefeller, you know. Not yet, anyway.
我不是洛克菲勒，还没

01:33:57.480 --> 01:33:59.150
So you owe me.
你欠我

01:34:00.400 --> 01:34:02.860
Listen, go down to the ball game tonight?
今晚去看球赛吗？

01:34:03.360 --> 01:34:06.630
I couldn't make it. I got things. I'll tell you about them.
我去不了，有事做，我会跟你说他们的事

01:34:07.560 --> 01:34:10.870
You're kidding. What was the score? Three to two?
你开玩笑，比分多少？三比二？

01:34:12.240 --> 01:34:13.460
Mel, guess what.
梅尔，猜猜怎么了

01:34:13.560 --> 01:34:15.390
My Little League team, the Little Lopezers,
我的小联盟球队，小罗培兹们

01:34:15.520 --> 01:34:17.230
they won the division tonight.
今晚赢得分区冠军

01:34:17.360 --> 01:34:19.660
That's great. Congratulations.
那很好，恭喜

01:34:20.080 --> 01:34:22.910
What'd you do, fix the umpire?
你怎么办到的，贿赂裁判？

01:34:25.840 --> 01:34:28.400
Jesus Christ.
老天

01:34:30.320 --> 01:34:32.230
Tony, what happened to you?
东尼，你怎么了？

01:34:35.080 --> 01:34:38.030
They wanted to spoil my $800 suit.
他们想毁了我八百块一套的西装

01:34:39.080 --> 01:34:41.190
Who the fuck did this?
哪个王八蛋干的？

01:34:41.840 --> 01:34:44.510
Hitters. I don't know.
杀手，我不知道

01:34:45.600 --> 01:34:47.750
Somebody must've brought them in.
一定是有人请来的

01:34:48.400 --> 01:34:50.230
I've never seen them before.
我从来没见过他们

01:34:50.600 --> 01:34:51.990
Hello, Mel.
哈啰，梅尔

01:34:53.400 --> 01:34:55.190
Got an answer to this, too?
你知道是怎么回事吗？

01:34:56.240 --> 01:34:59.590
-There always is, Tony.   -I'll bet it was the Diaz brothers.
-总会知道的，东尼  -一定是迪亚兄弟

01:34:59.720 --> 01:35:02.510
They got a beef going back to the Sun Ray thing.
他们的人在查阳光旅馆的事

01:35:03.720 --> 01:35:07.750
Maybe you're right, you know?
你可能是对的，你知道吗？

01:35:08.200 --> 01:35:12.750
Anyway, I'm glad you made it, Tony.
我很高兴你没事，东尼

01:35:13.800 --> 01:35:16.870
We'll return the favor for you in spades.
我们会好好报答你

01:35:16.960 --> 01:35:19.750
I'll take care of this myself.
我会自己搞定

01:35:25.600 --> 01:35:27.470
What is the gun for, Tony?
这枪是干嘛，东尼？

01:35:28.440 --> 01:35:31.150
What, this? It's nothing.
这个？没什么

01:35:32.800 --> 01:35:37.110
I'm... How do you say? Paranoid.
我…怎么说的？神经过敏

01:35:51.480 --> 01:35:53.310
You gonna answer, Frank?
你要接吗，法兰克？

01:35:55.480 --> 01:35:59.150
It must be Elvira. She got mad after we left the club.
一定是艾薇拉，我们离开俱乐部后，她大发脾气

01:36:02.320 --> 01:36:04.230
I'll tell her you're not here, okay?
要我跟她说你不在吗？

01:36:04.360 --> 01:36:08.140
No, it's all right. I'll talk to her.
不用，没关系，我跟她说

01:36:16.160 --> 01:36:17.350
Hello.
哈啰

01:36:24.160 --> 01:36:27.590
It's all right. I'm gonna be home in an hour. Don't worry.
没关系，我一个小时后回家，别担心

01:36:30.600 --> 01:36:33.830
Frank, you're a piece of shit.
法兰克，你是个人渣

01:36:33.960 --> 01:36:37.550
-What are you talking about?   -You know what I'm talking about,
-你在说什么？  -你知道我在说什么

01:36:37.680 --> 01:36:40.140
you fucking cockroach.
你这个他妈的鼠辈

01:36:40.280 --> 01:36:43.190
What are you talking about? Listen to me, huh.
你在说什么？听我说

01:36:43.320 --> 01:36:45.550
You know what a chazer is, Frank?
你知道凯泽是什么吗，法兰克？

01:36:46.560 --> 01:36:49.550
That's a pig that don't fly straight.
是只不正直的猪

01:36:50.680 --> 01:36:52.270
Neither do you, Frank.
你也一样，法兰克

01:36:53.840 --> 01:36:56.670
Tony, why the fuck would I hurt you?
东尼，我为什么要害你？

01:36:57.080 --> 01:36:58.710
I brought you in.
我带你入行的

01:36:58.840 --> 01:37:01.400
So we had a few differences, no big deal.
我们意见不同，那又怎样

01:37:02.720 --> 01:37:05.630
I gave you your start. I was the one who believed in you.
我给你机会开始，只有我相信你办得到

01:37:05.720 --> 01:37:07.910
I stayed loyal to you.
我对你忠诚

01:37:10.200 --> 01:37:13.710
I made what I could on the side, but I never turned on you, Frank!
我有做私活，但我从来没有背叛你，法兰克！

01:37:14.360 --> 01:37:15.390
Never!
从来没有！

01:37:19.120 --> 01:37:20.340
But you,
而你

01:37:23.920 --> 01:37:28.430
a man who ain't got his word is a cockroach.
不守信用，根本是个鼠辈

01:37:32.040 --> 01:37:34.750
Mel. Do something, will you?
梅尔，说句话，好吗？

01:37:39.120 --> 01:37:41.750
It's your tree, Frank. You're sitting in it.
那是你的问题，法兰克，你自己搞定

01:37:49.600 --> 01:37:52.790
All right, Tony. I was the one.
好吧，东尼，是我

01:37:59.600 --> 01:38:01.950
Please, give me a second chance.
给我一次机会

01:38:03.800 --> 01:38:06.630
Will you do that? Please?
好吗？拜托？

01:38:11.480 --> 01:38:15.230
Give me a second chance. I'll give you $10 million.
再给我一次机会，我可以给你一千万元

01:38:15.640 --> 01:38:18.990
Okay? $10 million.
好吗？一千万

01:38:19.640 --> 01:38:22.830
I got it in a vault over there in Spain, Tony.
我放在西班牙的保险库，东尼

01:38:23.000 --> 01:38:27.510
We go over there, we get on a plane, and it's yours.
我们过去，搭飞机过去，钱就都是你的了

01:38:28.200 --> 01:38:31.510
Okay? All of it. $10 million.
好吗？全部，一千万

01:38:32.440 --> 01:38:33.580
Okay, Tony?
好吗，东尼？

01:38:35.490 --> 01:38:36.700
Huh?

01:38:37.720 --> 01:38:39.030
Please, Tony?
拜托，东尼？

01:38:40.840 --> 01:38:44.030
Elvira? You want Elvira?
艾薇拉？你要艾薇拉？

01:38:44.840 --> 01:38:47.870
You can have her. I'll go away. I'm gonna disappear.
她可以跟你，我走，我会消失

01:38:48.000 --> 01:38:51.540
You'll never see me again. Please, Tony, I don't want to die.
你再也不会见到我，拜托，东尼，我不想死

01:38:51.680 --> 01:38:53.630
I never did nothing to nobody.
我从来没对别人怎样

01:38:53.800 --> 01:38:56.670
No, you never did nothing to nobody.
没错，你从来没对别人怎样

01:38:56.960 --> 01:38:58.870
You had somebody else do it for you.
你都是叫别人帮你做

01:38:59.000 --> 01:39:00.310
Oh, Tony, I'm begging you.
东尼，我求你

01:39:00.400 --> 01:39:04.180
-Get up! Get up now!   - Jesus! No! God!
-起来！起来！  -老天！不！老天！

01:39:09.200 --> 01:39:12.870
Look. Tony, no! Don't kill me, please.
拜托，东尼！别杀我，拜托

01:39:15.840 --> 01:39:17.230
I won't kill you.
我不会杀你

01:39:17.920 --> 01:39:19.910
-Oh, Christ, thank you.    -Get off my foot.
-感谢老天  -放开我的脚

01:39:20.040 --> 01:39:23.710
-Thank you.   -Manolo, shoot that piece of shit!
-谢谢  -马诺洛，开枪射这混蛋！

01:39:23.960 --> 01:39:25.350
No, no!
不，不！

01:39:25.720 --> 01:39:27.110
No!
不！

01:39:45.680 --> 01:39:48.550
Every dog has his day, huh, Mel?
罪有应得，对吧，梅尔？

01:39:48.680 --> 01:39:49.900
I told him
我跟他说过了

01:39:51.400 --> 01:39:53.270
it didn't make any sense
根本不合理

01:39:53.400 --> 01:39:57.230
clipping you when we had you working for us. He wouldn't listen.
你帮我们做事，为什么要除掉你，但是他不听

01:39:58.040 --> 01:40:01.870
He got hot tonight about the broad.
他今晚为了女人的事大发脾气

01:40:03.960 --> 01:40:05.390
He fucked up.
他犯下大错

01:40:06.200 --> 01:40:09.900
You, too, Mel. You fucked up.
你也是，梅尔，你也错了

01:40:11.120 --> 01:40:12.790
Don't go too far, Tony.
别太过分了，东尼

01:40:14.440 --> 01:40:17.190
I'm not, Mel. You are.
过分的不是我，梅尔，是你

01:40:26.040 --> 01:40:28.910
Fuck. You can't shoot a cop!
干，你敢杀警察！

01:40:30.480 --> 01:40:32.030
Whoever says you was one?
谁说你是警察？

01:40:32.120 --> 01:40:33.630
Wait a minute!
等等！

01:40:35.760 --> 01:40:37.950
You let me go. I'll fix this up.
你放我走，我会搞定这一切

01:40:38.440 --> 01:40:42.510
Sure, Mel. Maybe you can handle yourself
好啊，梅尔，或许你可以给自己安排

01:40:42.960 --> 01:40:46.270
one of them first-class tickets to the Resurrection.
参加最后审判的头等机票

01:40:46.800 --> 01:40:50.470
Fucking punk! Son of a bitch!
混蛋王八蛋！狗娘养的！

01:40:52.200 --> 01:40:54.990
-So long, Mel. Have a good trip.   -Fuck you!
-再见了，梅尔，玩得开心点  -去你妈的

01:41:01.800 --> 01:41:04.990
-Okay, come on.   -What about Ernie?
-走吧  -恩尼呢？

01:41:15.160 --> 01:41:16.830
You want a job, Ernie?
恩尼，要一份工作吗？

01:41:20.360 --> 01:41:23.510
-Sure, Tony.   -Okay, then you call me tomorrow.
-当然，东尼  -好，明天打电话给我

01:41:24.240 --> 01:41:26.070
Man, you got a job!
老兄，你被雇用了！

01:41:27.000 --> 01:41:29.830
Tony! Thanks.
东尼！谢谢

01:41:59.800 --> 01:42:00.860
Tony.
东尼

01:42:05.080 --> 01:42:06.910
God, what's happened?
老天，怎么回事？

01:42:09.200 --> 01:42:10.590
Where's Frank?
法兰克呢？

01:42:12.360 --> 01:42:14.070
Where do you think?
你说呢？

01:42:19.400 --> 01:42:22.870
Come on. Get your stuff.
把你的东西收一收

01:42:23.400 --> 01:42:24.910
You're coming with me.
跟我走

01:42:52.960 --> 01:42:59.110
这世界都是你的…

01:43:51.080 --> 01:43:52.830
美国三联银行

01:44:18.600 --> 01:44:20.710
蒙大拿管理公司

01:44:36.520 --> 01:44:39.150
吉娜蒙大拿发廊

01:47:02.000 --> 01:47:05.470
So you come to me with some kind of thing. Okay.
你有事来找我，没问题

01:47:05.560 --> 01:47:07.550
You propose it, I talk to you.
你提出来，我们谈谈

01:47:08.000 --> 01:47:11.270
But we got a problem. I can't pay more.
但是我有个问题，我不能付更多钱

01:47:12.440 --> 01:47:15.430
I'm bringing in twice as much as I ever did before.
我现在赚的钱是以前的两倍

01:47:15.640 --> 01:47:18.990
We're doing 10 million, 15 million a month. Come on.
我们一个月有一千万，一千五百万再进来

01:47:19.200 --> 01:47:21.230
That's serious money.
这是很大一笔钱

01:47:21.520 --> 01:47:23.310
You bank boys gotta come down a bit.
你们银行要降低费用

01:47:23.400 --> 01:47:24.430
No way.
不可能

01:47:24.520 --> 01:47:28.300
-That's crazy. We can't do that.   -Then that's too bad.
-这太超过了，我们办不到   -真糟糕

01:47:28.600 --> 01:47:31.910
-What am I gonna do?   -We're not a wholesale operation.
-那我要怎么办？  -我们不是大盘商

01:47:32.000 --> 01:47:35.620
We're a legitimate bank. The more cash you give me,
我们是合法的银行，你给我越多现金

01:47:35.760 --> 01:47:37.990
the harder it is for me to rinse.
我越难洗

01:47:38.480 --> 01:47:40.350
That's a problem. I didn't know.
有个问题，我不懂

01:47:40.440 --> 01:47:43.350
The fact is, I can't take any more of your money
情况是我不能再收你的钱

01:47:43.440 --> 01:47:45.790
unless I raise the rates on you.
除非我加你手续费

01:47:47.400 --> 01:47:49.230
-You gonna raise the...    -I gotta do it.
-你要加…  -非加不可

01:47:49.320 --> 01:47:50.510
The IRS is coming...
国税局有动作了…

01:47:50.600 --> 01:47:53.230
Don't give me that shit! Let's talk.
少跟我说那些废话！我们谈谈

01:47:53.360 --> 01:47:54.390
I'm talking.
谈谈吧

01:47:54.480 --> 01:47:56.940
I go low, you go high. I know the game.
我要降，你要加，我知道游戏规则

01:47:57.040 --> 01:47:59.600
-This is business talk.   -Let me explain something.
-商业讨论嘛  -让我解释一下

01:47:59.680 --> 01:48:02.140
The IRS is coming down heavy on South Florida.
国税局打算严查南佛罗里达

01:48:02.240 --> 01:48:04.620
There was a TIME magazine story that didn't help.
《时代》杂志上的一篇报导煽风点火

01:48:04.720 --> 01:48:06.190
There's a recession.
现在经济衰退

01:48:06.280 --> 01:48:08.580
I got stockholders I got to be responsible for.
我有股东，我要跟他们交代

